<L>__{exterior barricade night}
<A>__{marius reads the letter eponine has given him. he takes out pencil and paper and writes a note. looking round, he sees gavroche.}
<C>__{marius}
<D>__{gavroche! do you know the rue de l'homme arme?}
<C>__{gavroche}
<D>__{course i do!}
<C>__{marius}
<D>__{will you take this for me?}
<A>__{he holds out his note.}
<L>__{interior inn, rue de l'homme armee, paris night}
<A>__{the landlady climbs the stairs, followed by gavroche. the landlady indicates the door, and gavroche knocks boldly. the door opens a crack to reveal a cautious valjean.}
<C>__{gavroche}
<D>__{letter for cosette.}
<C>__{valjean}
<D>__{i will take it.}
<A>__{gavroche holds out the letter with one hand, not quite giving it, the other hand open for a tip. valjean gives him a coin, which he pockets as he hands over the letter.}
<C>__{gavroche}
<D>__{something for you, something for me. who needs charity?}
